This is an Elvis plugin for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Rolf Ahrenberg
                             < R o l f . A h r e n b e r g @ s c i . f i >

Project's homepage:          http://www.saunalahti.fi/~rahrenbe/vdr/elvis/

